                "caption": "",
                "credit": "",
                "url": "<blockquote>...the main features of interactive multimedia exhibits and Natural Users Interfaces (NUI) aiming at combining these two seemingly distant worlds through the development of an interactive multimedia installation provided with a natural interface...</blockquote>",
                "thumb": 	""
            },
            "text": {
                "headline": "Master of Science",
                "text": "<b>Cinema and Media Engineering</b></br></br>Thesis \"Natural User Interfaces for Interactive Multimedia Exhibits\"</br></br>- The first chapter is about the recent changes in exhibits</br>- The second chapter focuses on the human-computer interaction and on the principles that rule natural interfaces.</br>- The third chapter is based on a research on NUI, realised through interviews with various experts of different subjects, such as cognitive psychology, usability and interaction design.</br>- The fourth chapter goes on analysing both the software and hardware solutions useful for the creation of interactive multimedia exhibit installations.</br>- The fifth chapter is a short outlook on the future of NUI technologies and trends."
            }
